Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:10:00.70,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Water sprays into the air, going splish-splash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:04.33,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Like summer's never gonna end, at the poolside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:08.04,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky sparkles and shines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:13.80,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,All the girls have sweat on their skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:17.51,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Strip down to swimsuit? Can't decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:21.18,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I want us all to play innocently,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:26.35,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,too fond of being wet, just like children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:35.03,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,The paradise we dreamed of is like a resort if I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:38.36,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,That secret, stretched a bit too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:41.82,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, I fall on my rear, slip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:45.54,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a klutz every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:53.09,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Crying and laughing all the while,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:57.13,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,even if we tease, we're still friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:11:04.56,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,This exciting and beloved moment is a treasure for us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:10.44,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Onto that girl's smooth skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:14.73,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I splash some water, just to try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:18.15,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,She flicks back, plish plish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:24.74,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace that girl while she's still soaking wet.
