Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:03.64,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:08.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sleepy again today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:09.65,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:13.15,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, you don't seem sleepy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:16.03,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a morning person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:19.33,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be nice. I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:22.54,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just so bad with mornings...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:25.58,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:27.71,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Run-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:31.03,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's something strange about those birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:32.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:34.62,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:38.33,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Those birds keep going in circles. Are they okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:41.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan. That's a weather vane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:31.70,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Her silky long hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:35.41,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Her cute, thin, hourglass waist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:37.91,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Her arms as long as a giraffe's neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:40.09,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are they arguing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have more good points than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:44.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Her slender legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:46.68,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Better points!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.43,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Her voluptuous E-cups!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:49.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Her skin that's white as tofu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:51.65,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:56.11,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,More more more more more more more more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:53.87,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:56.11,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're naming your good qualities!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:59.25,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}H-How'd you get on that topic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:01.71,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Pores so small you'd need a microscope to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:03.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,A tiny face like a water flea's!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:06.62,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you're only describing her appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:10.90,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish they'd name some more internal good qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:11.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:13.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Her figure is to die for!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:21.19,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's wrong, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:22.59,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:26.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan keeps giving Yuuko all the praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:30.34,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I got so caught up in the moment that I shot myself in the foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:34.31,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, I'm sure you have good qualities, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:36.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:37.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:40.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:42.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people who are "moé" for f-flat chests.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:45.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, slender is in style!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your target audience, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:55.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so great about a nice body?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:06.90,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a model, Yuuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.55,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My goal for this year:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}lose two or three kilograms by summer, and look like a model!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:19.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, wait. I still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Summer doesn't really start until August.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:24.32,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The high school girl's summer has yet to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:27.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One more month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:29.29,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One more month to do something about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:31.87,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:42.42,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nagi, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I forgot something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:47.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A high school girl's summer starts today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:54.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Making us change into swimsuits just to clean the pool...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:55.90,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:04.18,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,But it sounds like fun to do the cleaning in swimsuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:06.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Don't you agree, Nagi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nagi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:12.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's tight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:21.37,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me I gained weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:23.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it couldn't possibly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.55,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did our swimsuits shrink?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:27.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine feels a bit tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:29.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still growing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,In various places.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:32.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it, gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:34.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My swimsuit shrunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:40.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Nagi's acting strange today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:43.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She's the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:01.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:02.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Making progress?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:04.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.69,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Yutaka's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.42,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Miho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:11.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, just like Yutaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:12.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fan of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:15.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:16.13,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:19.58,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I never got the chance to ask, but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:22.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,there's something I've been wondering about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:30.33,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this natural? Do you style it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:32.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:36.49,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Toooooruuun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.19,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Miporin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:41.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miporin, you're bothering Toorun, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:44.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't always cling to her like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.53,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair that you can touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka's gonna touch her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:53.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:56.03,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Toorun! Toorun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:56.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:07:00.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,you two seem like good friends. Were you in the same middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:01.57,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:04.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've sort of been stuck together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:10.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She keeps checking the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.63,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Three minutes is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:13.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Move away from Tooru-san immediately, Yutaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.15,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What, already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:20.70,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miporin, you're so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:22.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:26.17,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,so if Yutaka bothers you again, you can ask me for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:29.26,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:32.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,they used to call Miporin "Remote Control".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:33.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lame nickname, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:36.15,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You realize where that came from, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:38.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:44.73,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.10,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Miporin, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:48.41,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,But Toorun's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.92,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka never had a chance to touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:52.63,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru-san, I'll carry that trash bag for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Yutaka will carry it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.01,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, it's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:02.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up! This is heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:05.19,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miporin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.19,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\i1}"Remote Control."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:06.27,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The brilliant rays of sunlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:12.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,At the poolside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:14.64,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like a resort?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:21.64,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.57,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's way too hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.90,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The inside of a pool is sure hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:33.68,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:36.41,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The heat from the sun has nowhere to escape to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:44.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, let's get this over with!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:46.03,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.05,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:57.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:58.64,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:00.39,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, Nagi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:02.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is all slippery!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:14.57,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:17.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you fell and hit your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:19.41,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:20.43,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:23.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:24.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, you tell her too{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.13,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:37.97,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:40.43,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan! Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.18,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're soaked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:47.08,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it's gonna be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:49.90,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:51.69,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:54.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:00.87,A Channel 1 IN,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:04.50,A Channel 1 IN,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.10,A Channel 1 IN,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:35.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Toorun, what are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:39.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:46.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:50.32,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not paradise at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:58.53,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:16.75,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:20.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have put on more sunscreen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:26.89,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got a ton of exercise today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:31.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure it went down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:32.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rather,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:36.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I may have reached my goal of three kilograms already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.94,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Show me what I want, scale!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:12:59.88,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:03.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}since I'm wearing clothes, I should just subtract one kilogram.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:06.25,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh look, it hasn't changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:09.58,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a letdown after all my nervousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I should plan out my month.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:19.19,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with, limit your food intake and exercise a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:22.18,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat everything on your plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:25.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat dinner early and make it small.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:28.71,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cook something with lots of vegetables and that's low in fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:33.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to exercise daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:37.21,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Jogging, jumping rope, and stretching are effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:41.65,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, sadistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:44.88,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:52.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Better not tell anyone I started a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.40,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet they'd make a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:55.85,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Run found out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:59.87,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's bad for your health, so stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuuko would...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:05.54,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're fine the way you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:06.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.78,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sounds like something she'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tooru would...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:16.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:17.94,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mmm. Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:19.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Want some? You can have all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.87,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just imagining it is making me hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:28.91,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:32.36,A Channel 1,*,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I totally spaced out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:35.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru's kinda sharp, so I'd better watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:36.88,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:38.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:42.17,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:42.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:44.52,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on a diet, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:54.97,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.42,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Run and Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:00.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,They just went to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:03.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This spring, didn't you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:09.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,"If I diet, I can lose three kilograms by summer, no problem"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:11.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You were reminded of it yesterday, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:15.51,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You could have just forgotten a trivial thing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to tell the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:20.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't plan to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.64,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you want a bribe to keep quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:25.61,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:33.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Whah are you dohing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:42.45,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,For all the sweets you eat, you sure are skinny, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably because I run around so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:48.29,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, not much growth's going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.78,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.88,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,They say if you shake it, you lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:56.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I can't jog or jump rope or I'll lose my breasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:57.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.05,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're that concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:02.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you ask Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:06.11,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she actually goes to a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:09.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:11.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Some secret to her nice body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:12.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:14.88,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:15.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:22.40,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we just missed them somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, you're sweating!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:30.26,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,These are tears of sadness at being unable to see Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:32.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bluff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:34.01,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,All the walking made you hot, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.18,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:39.71,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's summer already. Why the long sleeves?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to avoid exposing my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:47.05,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, you'll get heatstroke, so take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:49.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that against it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:54.91,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Turn to page 52 in your textbooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:06.40,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Am I doing anything to maintain my figure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.19,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No particular reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.57,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just felt like asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.01,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:13.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:16.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I eat my favorite foods as much as I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:18.29,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,and sleep a lot, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:19.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:22.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, the ultimate model?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:22.97,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kid me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:24.31,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're utterly useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:24.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:28.40,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maintaining her figure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.57,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean a diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.39,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you were talking about a diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.85,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, did you start a diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:37.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:39.41,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:41.52,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the cat's out of the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:43.62,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, have you ever dieted?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.15,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Never stuck to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:49.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't like limiting what I eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:51.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither have you, right, Yuuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:53.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:56.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you have pets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Pets?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:58.03,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:18:01.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it again? Sounded like an office supply...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:03.41,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tapeworms!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:06.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You use the power of the tapeworms!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:09.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any, and they aren't pets!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:11.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:12.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:16.17,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can look up some good diets online.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:17.45,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:21.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd we come to the library?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.41,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you use the classroom's?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:27.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking this up on the classroom computer is kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:30.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are many kinds of diets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:36.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It says, "I lost 60 kg after taking this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:38.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:39.26,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:43.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I lost that much, my weight would go negative,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:45.89,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,and then I could fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:46.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:49.29,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd become incorporeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:52.69,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:55.55,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan, you're done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:56.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:59.49,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating less is fundamental to a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.26,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:09.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.34,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pushing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:15.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget what just happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:19.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that. I definitely heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:22.34,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:31.63,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I still get hungry by this time of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:33.81,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, hey, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:39.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Jumping right into a tough diet is bad for you, so you should stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:44.57,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, just make it your goal for next year instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.65,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right, Nagi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:51.53,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:53.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:55.49,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't push myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:58.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop rushing and go at my own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:19:59.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:00.73,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:02.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go for ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:04.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the sound of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:05.69,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now wait just a minute here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:08.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't ice cream a bit out of place in this conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:11.43,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want chocolate chip and strawberry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:15.19,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Vanilla, and cheese, and yogurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:16.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all white!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:17.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:21.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of getting mint and raspberry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:22.32,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:31.75,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Rum raisin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I won't be dieting any time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:40.33,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:43.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hold on{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine just the way you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:48.63,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:51.89,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, you're just right the way you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're plenty cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:59.05,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of embarrassing line is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:20:59.91,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:02.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, Yuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:04.26,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:05.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I said wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:24.26,A Channel 1,*,0000,0000,0000,,Brand new socks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:26.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fluorescent yellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:28.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Those will stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:29.63,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:30.88,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:32.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:32.16,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:33.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:36.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you wearing loose socks?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:37.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,In this day and age...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:40.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh, these are new knee-socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:42.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,They just fall down easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:44.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,How skinny are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:56.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they have stoppers, they keep slipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:58.45,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some sock glue?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:21:58.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:02.52,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I was just a bit chubbier.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:05.09,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard something I can't let slide!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:06.41,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I said nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:08.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:10.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:19.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I was chubbier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.79,0:23:57.71,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really summer now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.71,0:24:00.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer means the pool, and the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:01.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're at the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.86,0:24:04.17,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,And the beach means swimsuits everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:05.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't get enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.95,0:24:08.03,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really a high school girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:11.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're all dying to see Yutaka in a swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.80,0:24:12.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.95,0:24:14.57,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on A-Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.57,0:24:15.21,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Beach"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.21,0:24:18.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yutaka's only dying to see Toorun in a swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.92,0:24:20.49,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, me too, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.49,0:24:22.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What, no comeback?
